{"tid":485442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丸龜買埋譚仔三哥","createTime":"2017-12-01T03:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T10:01:13.000Z","uid":18074,"like":63,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"5e8ba81cabe9b167b3d68d356202d44d29e29ffa","tid":485442,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"日本東利多控股(Toridoll)宣布，收購「譚仔三哥米線」100%股份。完成後，「譚仔三哥米線」繼續於東利多控股的香港分公司東利多控股有限公司旗下營運。<br />\n<br />\n完成後，東利多控股將持有108間分店，當中56間為「譚仔三哥米線」，另外52間為「譚仔雲南米線」，令東利多控股在香港雲南米線市場的佔有率擴大至約70%。「譚仔雲南米線」於5月時簽訂交易協議獲東利多控股收購。<br />\n<br />\n東利多控股表示，「譚仔三哥米線」及「譚仔雲南米線」為香港市場中領先的米線品牌，完成收購後，將善用資源以求發揮協同效應，並進一步擴展米線業務。<br />\n<br />\n東利多控股旗下亦設有丸龜製麵店。"},{"pid":"f4a88e6bbbd3a8e6a7033063cab9d5e3289cc16d","tid":485442,"uid":72009,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:15:23.000Z","msg":"Ｄ肉愈來愈少，不了"},{"pid":"8c367a2a551925e8c3f3e839bdc9fe99e5de459a","tid":485442,"uid":74012,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:16:45.000Z","msg":"日式豚骨湯叉燒米線"},{"pid":"edc6cfecbfb0c969f615346b3494631b290400c6","tid":485442,"uid":14599,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"呢鋪真係溝埋變瀨尿牛丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad3f31b2da3f1d5d7c621122a4e26a1da9f1aeb","tid":485442,"uid":143241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"三哥失業了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5220127552430db2a42cf577bfc86c2a3b173517","tid":485442,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 合拼啦"},{"pid":"2feeaaed29ab13412dbf46ff4ef9259348619c83","tid":485442,"uid":42820,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTi